                    <span>Pretty pictures and informational text, can't ask for much more than that right? Vayo is not a writer by trade, but she certainly knows the business of photography--and customer service. This book is a quick how-to read for anyone interested in the business of senior portrait photography, and the themes can be carried over to pretty much any other form of commercial photography. She just knows what she's talking about.</span>
                  
